cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for building a knowledge graph from natural language definitions. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves classification and graph representation, which are common topics in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses text entailment recognition, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
